snippet.title: Spike Volleyball | Motion Capture : The Spike
snippet.description:
In this new video, Black Sheep Studio shows us how all volleyball techniques were recorded for the making of the first indoor volleyball simulation videogame.

🗓️ Spike Volleyball will be available on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and PC starting February 5th, 2019!
